name: Alien EMT
description:
Made in 2 days by Jim and Shawn for Ludum Dare 46!

Theme: Keep it Alive!

Rescue as many aliens as you can by picking them up and bringing them to the hospital before they die!

Scroll wheel: Zoom in and out

(Alternative Zoom - W - Zoom In - S - Zoom Out)

Click Mouse - move space ambulance

Tap Alien - use medicine (gives you more time!)
